<% provide(:title, "Girl Develop It 2017 Leadership Summit") %>

<div class= "summit">

  <section class="summit-hero">
    <div class="summit-logo">
	    <%= image_tag 'summit-logo-2017.png', alt: '2017 Girl Develop It Summit Logo' %>
    </div>
    <div class="underlined-headline">
        <h2>2018 Leadership Summit</h2>
        <hr>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-gdi text-block">
    <p>Girl Develop It is a 501(c)3 nonprofit that provides affordable and accessible opportunities to women who want to learn web and software development through hands-on instruction. Since our founding in 2010, Girl Develop It has led the nationwide movement to provide women with avenues to participate in the technology industry today.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="divider">
    <%= image_tag 'flourish.png'%>
  </section>

  <section class="about-summit text-block">
    <p>From September 13th - 16th in Chicago, Illinois, the annual Girl Develop It Leadership Summit will bring together 100 industry-leading technical women from our 58+ chapters across the country, representing more than 100,000 Girl Develop It members nationwide. The goal of the Summit is to provide our leaders with opportunities to connect, and to receive training and support in order to empower them to continue as ambassadors of GDI's mission, serve as leaders in their communities and the industry. The Summit features workshops on marketing, inclusive outreach, building a leadership team, effective storytelling and much more.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="divider">
